title: Web Developer (React.js)
job_overview:
We are looking for a React.js Web Developer to build a responsive website with under 10 pages for our social network community. Must have frontend development experience, API integration skills, and an eye for design. Familiarity with React Native Web is a bonus. The project is expected to take 2-4 weeks.
